        "content": "type: search_result\ntitle: Tenant checklist | Real Estate Agent Berlin\nurl: \"https://aden-immo.com/en/rent/tenant-checklist/\"\ndescription: \"Questions for the landlord: Don’t hesitate to ask questions during the viewing. For example: What were the last heating costs and service charges for the apartment? How many people are the service charges calculated for?\"\npage_age: 3 weeks ago\nprofile_name: ADEN Immobilien\nmeta_url_favicon: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/03L6jEx9BHwMuYtEmB5f4AELHOuSa17CwkVwR7NQOno/rs:fit:32:32:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cDovL2Zhdmlj/b25zLnNlYXJjaC5i/cmF2ZS5jb20vaWNv/bnMvN2U3M2IwMTk5/MzA4Yjg0YmFjZTc3/YjY5MjJkZjk3YjMx/ZTY1YTQ0NjBjODll/Y2MwMDA0ZjZkNGVj/MDE4YjM0NC9hZGVu/LWltbW8uY29tLw\"\nthumbnail_src: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/HZeCOzlT8w0DoSjxk46_7obEAILN2MBx__jnSCUp4UE/rs:fit:200:200:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9hZGVu/LWltbW8uY29tL3dw/LWNvbnRlbnQvdXBs/b2Fkcy9pbW1vYmls/aWVuL2M3N2JhYjQ1/MDhiZTZjY2RkZWYy/ZGU4YTUxMjU1ZWRl/LTEtU3RhZ2luZy1X/b2huemltbWVyLmpw/Zw\"\nthumbnail_original: \"https://aden-immo.com/wp-content/uploads/immobilien/c77bab4508be6ccddef2de8a51255ede-1-Staging-Wohnzimmer.jpg\"\nextra_snippets: \"The checklist for tenants helps you not to overlook anything important when looking for an apartment and signing a contract. From preparing important documents and viewings to the tenancy agreement – a structured tenant checklist will help you keep track of everything and avoid costly mistakes.|Questions for the landlord: Don’t hesitate to ask questions during the viewing. For example: What were the last heating costs and service charges for the apartment? How many people are the service charges calculated for? Are there any rules about keeping pets or renovating when you move out?|This should record the condition of the apartment in detail when you move in. This protects both parties and prevents disputes. If there is no record, insist on one being drawn up. Don’t be afraid to ask questions about the contract or raise contentious points.|Make a note of any defects or damage. A well-kept apartment without hidden damage is worth its weight in gold. Equipment and technology: Ask about the type of heating (central or floor heating) and the year of construction of the heating system – this affects the heating costs.\"\nhash: 5e9d1eae4a61635c\nembed_ref: aden-immo.com-R4a\napp_id: web\nskill_id: search",
